@startuml
title Sequence - Chat AI with Hybrid Retrieval
actor User
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "API Server" as API
participant "RAG Script" as RAG
database "Postgres" as DB

User -> App : Gửi câu hỏi tự nhiên
App -> API : POST /chat/query
API -> RAG : query --json
RAG -> DB : Structured retrieval (SQL filters)
RAG -> DB : Semantic retrieval (vector search)
DB --> RAG : candidate places + chunk context
RAG --> API : intent + answer draft + place_ids
API -> DB : Fetch place summaries by place_ids
DB --> API : recommended_places
API --> App : answer + recommended_places
App --> User : Hiển thị trả lời và gợi ý
@enduml
